entry.def: Something, usually something unpleasant, that is protracted lasts a long time, especially longer than usual or longer than you hoped.

example.ex: After protracted negotiations, Ogden got the deal he wanted...
example.tran: 经过长时间的谈判，奥格登得到了他想要的那笔生意。
